Our Idea (What is VIVAD X?)

Smart Document Reconciliation & Verification System
Rebuilds old manual document checking process used by banks, manpower agencies, consultancies, etc.
Upload multiple documents → AI scans & flags Red / Orange / Green → Verified fields signed on Tron Blockchain → Saved in company register

Main User Flow (Step by Step)

Signup
Company registers with: Company Name, Category (Bank / Manpower Agency / Consultancy / Insurance / Others), Email & Password
Data saved in PostgreSQL

Login
Company staff logs in to access their private dashboard
Simple email + password authentication

Playground / Verification Page
User selects or inputs Criteria (rules to check)
Upload 2–5 documents ( images and in futute pdf)
Click “Analyze”

AI Analysis & Results
System extracts important fields dynamically from documents
Shows color-coded results:
🔴 Red → Critical issues / Fraud risk
🟠 Orange → Warnings
🟢 Green → Verified correctly

Displays overall Risk Score (0–100)

Blockchain Signing
If mostly Green → System automatically hashes verified fields
Signs them on Tron Network (immutable proof)
Generates QR code for public verification

Verification Register
All successful verifications saved in company’s secure dashboard
Searchable history of all past checks

API Access (For Banks & Big Companies)
Banks can integrate via API (/api/v1/verify)
Send documents → Receive JSON with flags, score, and Tron hash


Criteria / Rules (Dynamic)

User can choose category (Bank KYC, Manpower, etc.) → System loads relevant rules
Or manually select fields to check (Name, Citizenship No., Amount, Expiry Date, License No., etc.)
Rules are dynamic and easy to extend

Problems This System Solves

Manual document checking takes too much time (30 min – 3 hours per case)
High human error and fraud risk
No proper audit trail (hard to prove verification later)
36,000+ pending DOFE cases and heavy workload on banks
Scattered documents with no reconciliation

Advantages of VIVAD X

Very fast — results in seconds instead of hours
Clear Red/Orange/Green visual flags (easy to understand)
Blockchain proof (Tron) → trusted by regulators and auditors
Works for all industries (Banks, Agencies, Consultancies, etc.)
Saves 50–70% staff cost
Dynamic rules → easy to customize
Privacy friendly (raw documents not stored permanently)
Good for both small companies (dashboard) and big banks (API)


